"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-05-03-ecl-unai-emery-explains-why-aston-lost-4-2-to-olympiakos\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Aston Villa manager, Unai Emery, has given reason his team were beaten 4-2 against Olympiakos in the first leg of their Europa Conference League, ECL, semi-final on Thursday .\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 194, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.402032997478061e-15, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 40, \"end\": 50, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Unai Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\"}, {\"begin\": 146, \"end\": 163, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.0162842983942805e-26, \"text\": \"Conference League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Europa_Conference_League\"}, {\"begin\": 165, \"end\": 168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emitter-coupled_logic\", \"score\": 0.9998787400611473, \"rank\": 0.00010514338876999911, \"text\": \"ECL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emitter-coupled_logic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emitter-coupled_logic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi's hat-trick ensured Olympiakos stunned Aston Villa at Villa Park.\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayoub El Kaabi\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ayoub_El_Kaabi\"}, {\"begin\": 231, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999895503606, \"rank\": 1.0448748573266006e-08, \"text\": \"Olympiakos\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympiacos_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 250, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.402032997478061e-15, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ollie Watkins and Moussa Diaby did score for Emery's side during the encounter.\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 278, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ollie_Watkins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ollie Watkins\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ollie_Watkins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ollie_Watkins\"}, {\"begin\": 296, \"end\": 308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Moussa Diaby\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Moussa_Diaby\"}, {\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"score\": 0.999999988418722, \"rank\": 1.1581357236980672e-08, \"text\": \"Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after the game, Emery said Aston Villa did not play well against the visitors, adding that they did not have control of the game.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 384, \"end\": 389, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"score\": 0.999999988418722, \"rank\": 1.1581357236980672e-08, \"text\": \"Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ray_Emery\"}, {\"begin\": 395, \"end\": 406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.402032997478061e-15, \"text\": \"Aston Villa\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aston_Villa_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are frustrated and disappointed, we did not play well,\\\" Emery said at his post-match interview.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is the summary I can do at the beginning.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We did not have control of the game.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were playing so fast.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In a lot of moments we needed to stop them getting good positions and get into their box with more passes than one, two or three.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 841, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And they were attacking, playing so open.\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our plan was completely different.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Congratulations, they deserve to win the first leg.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will try to come back but, of course, they are now favourites.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We will play there and try to show something different to tonight.\\\"\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The return leg will take place next week.\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ilechukwu backs Finidi to succeed with Super Eagles  EPL: Man Utd receive double injury boost ahead of Crystal Palace trip  EPL: Unai Emery names team that will not finish in top 5 after Villa lose to Everton  EPL: Why I did not shake hands with Mikel Arteta after Arsenal's 4-1 win - Villa boss, Unai Emery  EPL: Why Aston Villa lost 4-1 to Arsenal - Unai Emery  EPL: Why we beat Arsenal - Aston Villa manager Unai Emery  EPL: Unai Emery names favourites to win title ahead of Aston Villa vs Arsenal  ECL final: We played together - Maresca singles out one Real Betis player  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1759, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1190, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Super Eagles\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1204, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.527852184871324e-26, \"text\": \"EPL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Premier_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1280, \"end\": 1290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unai_Emery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Unai Emery\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\":